# Test 1: Basic functionality
ADDTEAM TeamA
ADDTEAM TeamB
ADDTEAM TeamC
START DURATION 100 PROBLEM 3
SUBMIT A BY TeamA WITH Accepted AT 10
SUBMIT B BY TeamB WITH Wrong_Answer AT 20
SUBMIT B BY TeamB WITH Accepted AT 30
SUBMIT C BY TeamC WITH Accepted AT 40
FLUSH
QUERY_RANKING TeamA
QUERY_RANKING TeamB
QUERY_RANKING TeamC
QUERY_SUBMISSION TeamA WHERE PROBLEM=A AND STATUS=Accepted
QUERY_SUBMISSION TeamB WHERE PROBLEM=B AND STATUS=Accepted
QUERY_SUBMISSION TeamC WHERE PROBLEM=ALL AND STATUS=ALL

# Test 2: Freeze and Scroll
FREEZE
SUBMIT A BY TeamA WITH Wrong_Answer AT 50
SUBMIT A BY TeamA WITH Accepted AT 60
SUBMIT C BY TeamC WITH Wrong_Answer AT 70
SCROLL

# Test 3: Multiple problems and penalty calculation
SUBMIT A BY TeamB WITH Wrong_Answer AT 80
SUBMIT A BY TeamB WITH Wrong_Answer AT 90
SUBMIT A BY TeamB WITH Accepted AT 100
FLUSH

END